I found this to be invaluable when I was tuning up my '79...

http://www.oldvolkshome.com/ignition.htm

Looks like 5 deg ATDC is right.  Check your engine code behind the oil
breather in case (like my bus) the PO rebuilt the engine with an older
fan housing.  Yours should be AW (1.8) or ED (2.0)

